TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,7,1);
$b = random(2,7,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The expression \(($a\sqrt{x}+$b\sqrt{y})($a\sqrt{x}-$b\sqrt{y})\)equals
\(Ax+By\) $BR where \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $a*$a;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  -$b*$b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

